<section class="about-shell">
  <div class="about-hero container-shell">
    <div class="about-hero-title">
      <p class="section-label">Introduction</p>
      <h1 class="about-display-title"><%= page.title %></h1>
    </div>

    <div class="about-intro-shell container-reading">
      <div class="about-intro-copy">
        <div class="article-prose about-prose-intro">
          <%- page.content %>
        </div>

        <blockquote class="about-quote">
          “Design is the silent ambassador of your brand's soul.”
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="about-expertise">
    <div class="container-shell">
      <div class="about-section-head">
        <h2 class="about-section-title">核心能力 / Expertise</h2>
        <p class="section-label">Editorial Practice</p>
      </div>

      <div class="expertise-grid">
        <article class="expertise-card">
          <p class="expertise-index">01 / CREATION</p>
          <h3>Digital Craft</h3>
          <p>从页面结构、内容承载到细节表达，关注数字产品如何在长期使用中依然保持清晰与质感。</p>
        </article>

        <article class="expertise-card">
          <p class="expertise-index">02 / INSIGHT</p>
          <h3>Visual Research</h3>
          <p>持续研究编辑感、阅读体验和品牌气质之间的关系，让视觉不止是表面，而成为理解的一部分。</p>
        </article>

        <article class="expertise-card">
          <p class="expertise-index">03 / SYSTEM</p>
          <h3>Curated Thought</h3>
          <p>把设计、技术与写作组织成一个可持续的系统，让内容表达、更新机制与前端质感彼此协同。</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-contact container-shell">
    <p class="section-label about-contact-label">Get In Touch</p>
    <h2 class="about-contact-title">期待与同样追求秩序、审美和长期价值的人产生共振</h2>

    <div class="about-contact-links">
      <a href="#">Instagram</a>
      <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="mailto:hello@example.com">Email</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</section>
